r-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称<em>对业务结果的影响极小</em>，</a>而观众也对Dokibird表示支持。 ・我们不仅在扩大我们的影响力不仅针对粉丝，也针对各种公司和组织。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="pguJ2lQbmh"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/">大约127,300人观看了VTuber Dokibird的“回归广播”，该广播被认为是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“约 127,300 人观看了 VTuber Dokibird 的《Return Broadcast》，该节目被认为是 Seren Ryugetsu 的表演者/声音模型” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/embed/#?secret=jK8AqDHD8f#?secret=pguJ2lQbmh" data-secret="pguJ2lQbmh" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://youtube.com/@Dokibird" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多奇鸟</a>/<a href="https://x.com/dokibird" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多奇<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3c6.png" alt="🏆" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a></p> <cite>YouTube/X（推特）</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="0C0SJxpDot"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-believed-to-be-selen-tatsuki-actor-call-attention-to-her-spoof-x-account/">VTuber Dokibird（据信是Selen Tatsuki的演员）呼吁关注她的恶搞X账户</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restric