 ANYCOLOR NIJISANJI EN（新）活动推迟；一系列批评可能产生影响https://p2y.jp/anycolor-has-postponed-nijisanji-en-new-event-possible-due-to-a-series-of-criticism-effects/ https://p2y.jp/anycolor-has-postponed-nijisanji-en-new-event-possible-due-to-a-series-of-criticism-effects/#respondp2y_admin Sat, 10 Feb 2024 08:20:09 +0000 VTuberバーチャルNIJISANJI EN(新)Selen Tatsuki(セレン龍月)TwitterYouTuberにじさんじプロジェクトバーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=115052 <p> ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 2024（令和6）2月10日，该公司运营的VTuber团体NIJISANJI EN（新）举办了活动“马里奥赛车8豪华特别版[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-has-postponed-nijisanji-en-new-event-possibly-due-to-a-series-of-criticism-effects/">ANYCOLOR 的 NIJISANJI EN（新）活动推迟；一系列批评可能产生的影响</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> <strong>ANYCOLOR株式会社</strong>于2024年2月10日（令和6）宣布，该公司运营的VTuber团体<strong>NIJISANJI EN（新）</strong>的活动“马里奥赛车8豪华特别战”将延期举行。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="115060" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-has-postponed-nijisanji-en-new-event-possibly-due-to-a-series-of-criticism-effects/anycolor_has_postponed_nijisanji_en_new_event_possibly_due_to_a_series_of_criticism_effects/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/anycolor_has_postponed_nijisanji_en_new_event_possibly_due_to_a_series_of_criticism_effects.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="anycolor_has_postponed_nijisanji_en_new_event_possibly_due_to_a_series_of_criticism_effects" data-image-description="&lt;p>;ANYCOLOR社 NIJISANJI EN (新) のイベント開催を延期 一連の批判影響の可能性も&l